channel.title: My Account
channel.description:
EDIT - This is my Hybrid type thing EDIT - I bumped Because I down there, and I like it :P EDIT - I want to use him in BH what are good stats for BH... [center]
Money: You will need about 300k and to be members. First buy 1k Oak logs in the Grand Exchange at the maximum price. Make Oak Planks with your 1k Oaks and 250k you need. Sell your Oak Planks at the min price, you will now have about 500k! This will take 38 runs... This Method requires 10 crafting, thats right you guessed it ;). You also need about 89k buy flax for 89 ea then spin and sell at Lumbridge spinning wheel
[img]http://img469.imageshack.us/img469/5193/spacerqk8.jpg[/img]
[img]http://img237.imageshack.us/img237/3695/purehibe8.png[/img]
[img]http://img469.imageshack.us/img469/5193/spacerqk8.jpg[/img]
[b][u]The Story behind him[/u][/b]
Well It all started around When Ollie (Ooo Java) Started his pure "One to Zero." I had an account and I asked for info, despite being told hundereds of time scrap it it has defence, I wanted to get:
Attack: 60-70 Strenght: 85+ Defence: 20-40 Prayer: 52 Range: 96 Magic: 94
I gave up at because being told, no stop it, don't waste your time, I did waste my time, I might auto him up sometime to 50/60/40 and turn him into a mauler, then sell him to a friend... So i started again, I had an account, but was it worthy to be a pure?
I didn't want a pure, I wanted something that would smash anything out of my way, The Hybrid... Yes its been around for along time but I love 'em. So it was set. I started training and posted a topic on here, It went well, the topic died, I kept training... and now I'm here...
[img]http://img469.imageshack.us/img469/5193/spacerqk8.jpg[/img]
[u][b]Wanted Levels:[/b][/u]
[b]Attack:[/b] 60 [b]Strenght:[/b] 99 [b]Defence:[/b] 1 [b]Prayer:[/b] 31 [b]Range:[/b] 96 [b]Magic:[/b] 94
Yes these levels seem OTT but I have a plan:
[b][u]Plan[/u][/b]
[s]Start out at lumbridge and kill level 1 rats untill 20 attack and 20 strenght, then go to the monks in the monastery and train until 50 attack 50 strenght. OR go to the fleshcralwers untill 50 attack 50 strenght.[/s] Then go to the rock crabs then train to 85 strenght, then do the dragon wepons quests, then PC until 99 strenght.
[s]While getting 50 attack and 50 strenght you could of got 40 range with throwing knifes and done dwaf multi cannon quest.[/s] Get least 60 magic, starting with: from level 1 magic wear full iron armour and a air staff and also you need about 50k mind runes, split half and half with a friend and both wear full iron, get your magic bonus as low as possible, then cast and you get 5 xp per mind rune eh? Thats 125000 xp, in it self that is 52 magic, that would take month or six... to get from 1 to 25 magic it takes 12302.4 mind runes... so 12303 mind runes..., so do that untill 45 magic, then cammy tele till 55 then alch.
So far: Attack: [s]10 20 30 40 50[/s] Current: 50 Strength: [s]10 20 30 40 50[/s] Current: 51 Defense: [s]1[/s] Current: 1 Prayer: [s]10 20[/s] Current: 26 Magic: [s]10 20 30 40[/s] Current: 42 Range: [s]10 20 30 40 41 42 43 44[/s] Current: 45
